10 sole proprietorship in good legal standing that specializes in the
11 construction, installation, maintenance, and repair of underground
12 infrastructure systems including water, sanitary sewer, storm or
13 drainage sewer, or gas, on behalf of a utility owner or the property
14 owner; and
15 10. "Variance and Appeals Board" means the Oklahoma State
16 Plumbing Installation Code Variance and Appeals Board.
17 SECTION 2. AMENDATORY 59 O.S. 2021, Section 1017, is
18 amended to read as follows:
19 Section 1017. The provisions of The Plumbing License Law of
20 1955 shall not apply to:
21 1. Minor repairs, consisting of repairing or replacing faucets
22 or minor working parts of plumbing fixtures;
23 2. Farm buildings located outside any city or town unless such
24 buildings are connected to a public water or sewer system;
SB1035 HFLR Page 4
BOLD FACE denotes Committee Amendments.

1 3. Maintenance work for state institutions and school
2 districts;
3 4. The installation, maintenance, repair, renovation of
4 automatic sprinkler systems and related mechanical appurtenances
5 beginning at a point where the pipe or piping system provides water
6 used exclusively for these automatic sprinklers and their related
7 appurtenances and to standpipes connected to automatic sprinkler
8 systems;
9 5. The construction, installation, maintenance, repair,
10 renovation, and/or or removal of pipe or piping systems and related
11 mechanical appurtenances including backflow preventers, appliances
12 and/or or equipment used in connection therewith, directly or
13 indirectly within or without any building or structure, from a point
14 or location in a source of potable water supply at which point or
15 location there exists any backflow preventer, provided that said the
16 pipe and/or or piping systems are for:
17 a. heating, except radiant-floor heating systems as
18 defined provided for in subparagraph d of paragraph 9
19 8 of Section 1003 of this title,
20 b. cooling,
21 c. air conditioning,
22 d. refrigeration, or
23 e. boilers and other pressure vessels of whatsoever any
24 kind and character.
