23 a. plumbing work consisting of installing, servicing, or
24 repairing service mains, service lines, or sewer, gas,
SB1035 HFLR Page 6
BOLD FACE denotes Committee Amendments.

1 or storm drainage services on private property in an
2 area that extends from a public right-of-way or public
3 easement to not less than five (5) feet from a
4 building or structure,
5 b. downspout boots, or
6 c. fire risers.
7 Work performed pursuant to paragraph 7 of this subsection shall
8 be done under the scope of the bond of the utility contractor and
9 shall not be done on repairs on previous work completed by a
10 plumbing contractor.
11 SECTION 3. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
